<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 13:45:31 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a072378a1085</link><description>&lt;p&gt;#FensterFreitag&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Looking through a window covered in water drops. The background is blurred, but one can identify some hills on different shades of green and a very grey sky. The landscape is displayed upside-down in every droplet. " height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a072378a1085.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 13:45:31 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a070472d38c9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我们花园里有一只狐狸，正抬头看着鸟食台——它在草地上吃了好一会儿东西。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A fox in our garden, looking up at the bird table - spent a while eating something from the grass." height="1366" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/pigpog/6a070472d38c9.jpg" width="2048"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://pigpog.some.pics"&gt;@pigpog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 11:33:09 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a070438610f9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我们花园里的一只狐狸——花了点时间在吃草里的什么东西。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A fox in our garden - spent a while eating something from the grass." height="1471" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/pigpog/6a070438610f9.jpg" width="2048"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://pigpog.some.pics"&gt;@pigpog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 11:32:11 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a070034753ae</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在我的院子里有一家乌鸫，这些天它们非常活跃，正在为幼鸟捕捉蚯蚓。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="En mi patio hay una familia de mirlos, y están muy activos estos días cazando lombrices para sus crías." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/hiddenflair/6a070034753ae.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://hiddenflair.some.pics"&gt;@hiddenflair&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 11:15:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a06d41034532</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🏃🏻 雨中晨跑&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="🏃🏻 Rainy morning run" height="1486" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/atog/6a06d41034532.jpg" width="1179"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://atog.some.pics"&gt;@atog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 08:06:43 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>